data.description: Fabulous Gold Fortified four bedroom, three and one-half bath home in Stonegate Estates! The kitchen features granite counter tops and stainless appliances, breakfast area and separate dining area. The living area offers a tray ceiling, the master suite offers a tray ceiling, walk-in closet, double vanity in the master bath, separate shower and 60 inch hydro-therapeutic walk-in bathtub. Enjoy the ultimate grilling and chilling in your fenced yard. Stonegate Estates is conveniently located on Coastal Gateway Boulevard about mid-way between Highway 59 and the Foley Beach Express. Minutes to shopping, OWA, beaches, entertainment & restaurants! This subdivision is gated and offers a community pool and two tennis courts.
